<header>
  <h1>Self-Check Quiz</h1>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="card">
    <ul>
      <li>Do I feel stressed most days?</li>
      <li>Do I struggle with sleep?</li>
      <li>Do I feel overwhelmed?</li>
      <li>Do I avoid assignments?</li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Mostly Yes:</strong> You may need support</p>
    <p><strong>Mostly No:</strong> You are managing well</p>
  </div>
</section>

